column5: Heading for Couch tomorrow morning...planning on hitting Airport Rd.  around 7:15-7:30 AM. Anyone interested in trying to hunt down a feed of perch shoot me a PM...I will be going for sure...and will be checking  for reply's until around 10 PM tonight.
I'm on the couch right now..
Where abouts is Airport Rd.?  I'm not all that familiar with Couch.  Can't go tomorrow, but might think about Fri....maybe....  Maureen

Maureen Airport Rd is about 3 miles east of the Casino. Email me if you are interested for friday. Also check the weather forecast..it is supposed to be cold...Wouldn't want the fuel to gel up in your VW.
ok, so that's about an hour so so from me give or take....I'll give it some thought today Steve and let you know....good luck to you today.  Maureen

CPH... Wish I could make it man!.... Hey could you do me a favour while there though?? Could you look at St.John? and let me know the ice situation? it is just up airport road just past the tracks... Or you could use the Soap factory launch to spy on it.  Thanks brother!  Gerritt.
